title: Converse Takeaway Show from Pitchfork Paris: How To Dress Well "And It Was You"
description:
After his set at Pitchfork Paris, How To Dress Well stepped outside in the rain to perform this Takeaway Show for La Blogotheque, Pitchfork TV, and Converse.

Track: "And It Was You"
